In each case, the analysis will be divided in two parts. First,
the brane probe analysis will be carried out. Notice that, in general,
the Killing spinors for the supersymmetries of the brane probe
embeddings must be a subset of those corresponding to the  pure  pp-wave
configuration.  Hence in all cases we must have at least    the projection
